STATE of New Jersey IN the INTEREST OF A.A.J., a Juvenile. (A.A.J.-Petitioner) C-988 September Term 2016
079174 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000387-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
